Class BurpExtenderCallbacksMock

  • java.lang.Object

    public class BurpExtenderCallbacksMock
extends java.lang.Object
implements burp.IBurpExtenderCallbacks
    Simple class implementing IBurpExtenderCallbacks to mock Burp's behavior for extender callbacks to be able to write according unit tests.
